{
  "stem": "4693.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he approached Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Korfanty, because he knew her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And who it was-- it was General Sikorski, who later became the head of the Polish government in exile.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And who later was bumped up by Churchill, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because Churchill gave him plenty of undertakings, and he didn't know how to get out of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he had some documents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said that he will try-- illegally-- to get through to France, to Hungary and France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it wsa the last I I saw of him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He succeeded-- got to Paris and became the head of the Polish Committee, and then Polish government in exile.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stayed and moved further north, going towards Wilno.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And two days later, the Russians came and took over the eastern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Obviously, they came to Sarny, this was the place that we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took the car, what have you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For the first time, I saw the russian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from Sarny, they-- few days later by train-- we got to Wilno.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Wilno one looked at the possibility, eventually, to get to Sweden, and to escape this way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "While I was in Wilno, some disturbing news were coming from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I did the-- an agreement was made between the Russians and the Lithuanians, that the Lithuanians would take over Wilno.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was frightened that I wouldn't get-- that I would be completely blocked-- that the Germans, in due course, would take it over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I decided to go south, and I went to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from Bialystok, I didn't have any news from my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I did a very daring thing-- I went between the Russian and German lines, on the Bug River, to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was caught by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
